      "writtenOn": "2020-08-18T02:02:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I talked to the DLC team today and got a better idea of how we\u0027ll do this. We need to update our ocr ebuild to inherit from the dlc eclass and then add the ocr USE flag to a board to include it. We\u0027ll most likely start with eve since it already supports DLC. Then, we\u0027ll need to update our tast test to install the DLC using dlc_util.go before running the rest of the test. With all of that in place, the ocr tast dependency defined here will signify that a board is capable of installing the ocr DLC package and running the test. Please let us know if you\u0027d like any other info.",
      "parentUuid": "e90866d5_7923cf6b",
      "revId": "ad0ac6fc968e9c07f276d2f659106d22a770ae4b",
